title: The Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show Podcast
itunes:title: The Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show Podcast
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3:

Clay and Buck talk with new syndicated radio host Jesse Kelly, who has replaced Buck in his 3-6PM ET slot. More on movies that put you in a July 4th kind of mood. Rush's Timeless Wisdom: Independence Day Education. Clay and Buck on how liberals have destroyed the history of America's founding. Open Line Friday calls finish off the program.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
